INSTALLATION
    Sara can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions. Please also have a look at the file "REQUIREMENTS" for
    information on the tools required to run, compile, and develop Sara.


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of Sara. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/sara/sara.pdf>.
